1
00:01:24,780 --> 00:01:29,580
=Fights Break Sphere=

2
00:01:40,220 --> 00:01:43,420
=Episode 16=

3
00:01:43,420 --> 00:01:48,140
Of course! The Mo Clan definitely has the best contraptions in
the world. I just need to point this gently in your direction.

4
00:01:48,140 --> 00:01:50,920
It doesn't matter how high your Fight Qi level is,
how fast you can fly, or how far you can run.

5
00:01:50,920 --> 00:01:52,820
Let's go.

6
00:01:52,820 --> 00:01:54,550
I will be able to shoot you down.

7
00:01:54,550 --> 00:01:57,100
Right. This weapon of mine--

8
00:02:08,230 --> 00:02:11,600
Husband, why isn't that person chasing after us?

9
00:02:11,600 --> 00:02:14,620
Who knows? Maybe he's an idiot.

10
00:02:14,620 --> 00:02:16,490
Run as fast as you can.

11
00:02:37,810 --> 00:02:42,080
You two idiots.
Tell me, what are you trying to do?

12
00:02:42,080 --> 00:02:44,120
Let me out!

13
00:02:50,570 --> 00:02:54,480
What's this you're playing with?
Can you show it to me?

14
00:02:54,480 --> 00:02:56,770
We're not even part of the Snake People Tribe.
Why are you trapping us?

15
00:02:56,770 --> 00:02:59,450
This fire is pretty interesting.

16
00:02:59,450 --> 00:03:01,870
Right. I forgot to tell the two of you,

17
00:03:01,870 --> 00:03:05,260
this net was made from fragments of stars.

18
00:03:05,260 --> 00:03:08,840
The material is Heavenly Iron.
No matter how strong your Fight Qi is,

19
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:11,880
you still won't be able to break any of the Mo Clan's things.

20
00:03:13,200 --> 00:03:15,530
What should we do, Husband?

21
00:03:17,660 --> 00:03:21,290
We just got lost in this barren desert and came over here
because we heard the sound of fighting.

22
00:03:21,290 --> 00:03:24,430
We hold no grudge against the Mo Clan.
Why don't you let us go?

23
00:03:24,430 --> 00:03:28,030
You're trespassing into the territory of the Mo Clan
and are very suspicious.

24
00:03:28,030 --> 00:03:31,030
But this flame is quite fascinating.

25
00:03:31,030 --> 00:03:33,830
Our Clan Head would really like it.

26
00:03:36,030 --> 00:03:39,520
But... you with the soft skin and tender flesh...

27
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:43,230
Our Clan Head may be a lot more interested in you.

28
00:03:45,440 --> 00:03:48,910
Don't even think about it. I belong to my Husband.

29
00:03:48,910 --> 00:03:51,750
Don't be carried away by wishful thinking.

30
00:03:51,750 --> 00:03:54,020
Husband, don't worry. Even if I were to die,

31
00:03:54,020 --> 00:03:56,220
I won't let them succeed.

32
00:03:57,970 --> 00:04:01,260
Don't worry. I won't let them touch you.

33
00:04:01,260 --> 00:04:03,030
What does it have to do with you?

34
00:04:03,030 --> 00:04:04,960
Why don't you have a look at your own appearance?

35
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:07,490
I'm talking about the youngster next to you.

36
00:04:55,000 --> 00:05:00,180
So, you're that young lad whose body possesses
the Essence Flame. Where are you from?

37
00:05:00,180 --> 00:05:03,470
We're siblings.
We came out here with our family to do business.

38
00:05:03,470 --> 00:05:06,670
The sandstorms here in this desert are too strong and so
we ended up wandering away from our family members.

39
00:05:06,670 --> 00:05:10,290
That's why we carelessly ended up
on your Mo Clan's grounds.

40
00:05:11,640 --> 00:05:13,590
- Siblings?
- Wife...

41
00:05:13,590 --> 00:05:16,450
Listen...

42
00:05:16,450 --> 00:05:18,960
They can't even tell lies.

43
00:05:20,730 --> 00:05:25,740
Why don't you show me whatever Essence Flame you have?

44
00:05:33,710 --> 00:05:37,620
Don't be impetuous. Only devils are impetuous.

45
00:05:37,620 --> 00:05:41,510
Regardless of how high your Fight Qi rank is,
if you lose your feet,

46
00:05:41,510 --> 00:05:43,840
would you be able to regrow them?

47
00:05:46,590 --> 00:05:51,780
What is binding your feet
is made of extremely sharp Heavenly Iron.

48
00:05:51,780 --> 00:05:56,030
If you fiddle around, then you have to be prepared
to say goodbye to your feet.

49
00:05:56,030 --> 00:06:00,540
Show me your Essence Flame.

50
00:06:12,390 --> 00:06:14,090
Beast Flame.

51
00:06:15,240 --> 00:06:17,740
Not bad at all.

52
00:06:19,520 --> 00:06:22,930
I'm the Head of the Mo Clan, Mo Cheng.

53
00:06:22,930 --> 00:06:24,840
Give that to me

54
00:06:24,840 --> 00:06:27,590
and I'll spare your life. How about it?

55
00:06:28,290 --> 00:06:32,170
Leader Mo Cheng, I'd also like to give this to you,
but this flame

56
00:06:32,170 --> 00:06:34,270
cannot be taken from within me.

57
00:06:35,710 --> 00:06:40,530
As for me, when I ate a purple lump of something
by chance, I gained this flame.

58
00:06:40,530 --> 00:06:44,330
Then, the only way for me is to cut an opening in your body

59
00:06:44,330 --> 00:06:47,240
and take it out.

60
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:50,590
Wouldn't I be dead then?

61
00:06:50,590 --> 00:06:52,790
That would be true, wouldn't it?

62
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:56,200
What are you going to do?

63
00:06:56,200 --> 00:06:59,870
Let me tell you, you dual-gendered demon!

64
00:06:59,870 --> 00:07:02,240
If you're capable, come charge at me.

65
00:07:03,570 --> 00:07:08,090
Charge at you? I'm afraid I'd dirty my hands.

66
00:07:09,090 --> 00:07:10,770
Come in, my subordinate.

67
00:07:14,770 --> 00:07:17,630
Clan Head, do you want the first cup or the second cup?

68
00:07:17,630 --> 00:07:23,620
The first cup... give it to that rude girl in green to drink.

69
00:07:25,310 --> 00:07:27,500
Husband, don't worry. Did you forget?

70
00:07:27,500 --> 00:07:30,190
I've consumed hundreds of poisons while growing up.

71
00:07:39,210 --> 00:07:40,650
Enough, enough, enough.

72
00:07:40,650 --> 00:07:42,500
Let me give you a cup.

73
00:07:50,300 --> 00:07:54,800
Sure. Looks like I'm lucky today.

74
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:58,990
I actually bumped into a person
with a body distressed from a poison within.

75
00:07:58,990 --> 00:08:01,350
If we refine him,

76
00:08:01,350 --> 00:08:06,180
he can be made into a very nice medicine cauldron.
Then we'll also refine her

77
00:08:06,180 --> 00:08:10,360
to make a very nice poisoned arrow.
It looks like today...

78
00:08:10,360 --> 00:08:13,450
You have delivered yourselves at my door.

79
00:08:15,490 --> 00:08:17,270
Clan Head!

80
00:08:22,340 --> 00:08:25,320
I'm busy now. What are you calling me for?

81
00:08:25,320 --> 00:08:28,350
The Lord said he can't wait any longer.

82
00:08:30,100 --> 00:08:34,830
All of those who died are from my Mo Clan.
What is there for him to be impatient about?

83
00:08:38,090 --> 00:08:40,460
Keep an eye on these two.

84
00:09:25,100 --> 00:09:27,110
Two fake persons!

85
00:09:29,950 --> 00:09:33,070
But, Husband, what should we do about these?

86
00:09:34,730 --> 00:09:38,090
The Beast Flame isn't workable. But there's also this.

87
00:09:40,070 --> 00:09:42,480
Bone Spirit Cold Flame.

88
00:09:46,150 --> 00:09:47,670
Greetings, Lord.

89
00:09:47,670 --> 00:09:51,640
What's happening?
Why haven't you continued to attack?

90
00:09:52,590 --> 00:09:56,410
The Snake People Tribe's foundation is deep
and the people are difficult to handle.

91
00:09:56,410 --> 00:10:00,610
Our Mo Clan has suffered
a great number of injuries and deaths.

92
00:10:00,610 --> 00:10:01,780
Lord,

93
00:10:01,780 --> 00:10:04,610
how about sending more of
the highly skilled Fight Practitioners?

94
00:10:04,610 --> 00:10:08,470
Wipe them out in one move.
Wouldn't that be better?

95
00:10:12,370 --> 00:10:15,570
I just knew that my husband was very amazing!

96
00:10:15,570 --> 00:10:17,530
But, Husband, since you are this amazing,

97
00:10:17,530 --> 00:10:21,740
why didn't you just use this fire to burn
that womanly-like person to death?

98
00:10:21,740 --> 00:10:24,780
I was considering it
but I don't know anything about his background.

99
00:10:24,780 --> 00:10:28,240
I also don't dare to attack him
without careful consideration.

100
00:10:28,240 --> 00:10:29,620
It's never wrong to be more cautious.

101
00:10:29,620 --> 00:10:30,920
Let's go. Let's hurry up and escape.

102
00:10:30,920 --> 00:10:32,910
Just... We're leaving just like this?

103
00:10:34,580 --> 00:10:36,350
- We're just going to–
- Shhh!

104
00:10:39,810 --> 00:10:41,160
- Stop right there!
- Stop right there!

105
00:10:41,160 --> 00:10:42,790
- Come quick! They're escaping!
- They're escaping!

106
00:10:42,790 --> 00:10:44,880
Stop! Don't run!

107
00:10:44,880 --> 00:10:46,380
- Catch them!
- Hurry! Go in!

108
00:10:46,380 --> 00:10:49,070
- Halt! - Don't let them get away.
Chase after them! - Go in...

109
00:10:50,770 --> 00:10:53,920
Hurry!

110
00:10:59,780 --> 00:11:01,200
Let's go!

111
00:11:02,380 --> 00:11:04,630
It's too late.

112
00:11:06,010 --> 00:11:09,960
Stop worrying about how many are injured and killed.
Keep on attacking!

113
00:11:09,960 --> 00:11:15,190
Lord, if all the disciples of the Mo Clan were to die, then

114
00:11:15,190 --> 00:11:18,250
there's no point in me being the Clan Head.

115
00:11:19,360 --> 00:11:21,880
According to our earlier plan,

116
00:11:21,880 --> 00:11:24,060
we'd attack in a methodical manner

117
00:11:24,060 --> 00:11:28,480
and capture Medusa alive, isn't that something
that will happen sooner or later?

118
00:11:28,480 --> 00:11:32,910
Medusa is preparing to swallow
the Green Lotus Earth Core Flame.

119
00:11:32,910 --> 00:11:35,350
If we really wait for her to succeed in
making the nine transformations,

120
00:11:35,350 --> 00:11:38,630
I'm afraid the Mo Clan will be eradicated by her.

121
00:11:38,630 --> 00:11:43,140
Yes... We will surely attack them before she devours
that Green Lotus Earth Core Flame.

122
00:11:43,140 --> 00:11:48,120
It's only that, Lord, this time around,
my Mo Clan has put forth such a great effort.

123
00:11:48,120 --> 00:11:51,450
After this matter is finished and Medusa is yours,

124
00:11:51,450 --> 00:11:55,320
please give us the Green Lotus Earth Core Flame.

125
00:11:55,320 --> 00:11:58,680
In the future, when Soul Hall attacks the Fight Qi Continent,

126
00:11:58,680 --> 00:12:00,440
our Mo Clan

127
00:12:01,660 --> 00:12:03,560
is willing to be your vanguard.

128
00:12:03,560 --> 00:12:05,040
Fine.

129
00:12:05,040 --> 00:12:10,310
I can even help you take in the Essence Flame
and let your power increase in bounds.

130
00:12:10,310 --> 00:12:11,580
Thank you, Lord.

131
00:12:11,580 --> 00:12:15,220
I've heard about that Green Lotus Earth Core Flame
for a long time.

132
00:12:15,220 --> 00:12:19,480
I just don't know if it's really
as mystical as they have said.

133
00:12:19,480 --> 00:12:24,800
Green Lotus Earth Core Flame was refined
by the Fight God especially for the Snake People Tribe.

134
00:12:24,800 --> 00:12:27,750
It's needless to talk about its mystical effect.

135
00:12:27,750 --> 00:12:32,790
As long as you're loyal to the Soul Hall,
I surely will help you.

136
00:12:32,790 --> 00:12:36,920
All right, Lord. Just wait for good news from me.

137
00:12:36,920 --> 00:12:42,550
Wait! Did you capture anyone and place them in your tent?

138
00:12:44,360 --> 00:12:48,690
Lord, they are just some captives
from the Snake People Tribe.

139
00:12:49,310 --> 00:12:51,070
Catch them!

140
00:12:52,180 --> 00:12:55,300
- Stop!
- It must be the captives trying to escape.

141
00:12:55,300 --> 00:12:58,220
Lord, I'll go take a look.

142
00:13:08,740 --> 00:13:10,870
Get out of the way...!

143
00:13:11,530 --> 00:13:14,440
My medicine cauldron! My poisonous arrow!

144
00:13:14,440 --> 00:13:17,440
You bunch of trash! Quickly, shoot the arrows!
Shoot the arrows!

145
00:13:17,440 --> 00:13:19,930
Ready! Shoot!

146
00:14:34,700 --> 00:14:37,890
Husband, a little higher!

147
00:14:42,140 --> 00:14:44,310
Be careful!

148
00:15:00,100 --> 00:15:01,520
Careful!

149
00:15:01,520 --> 00:15:03,250
Over there!

150
00:15:04,260 --> 00:15:06,380
Husband, there!

151
00:15:25,980 --> 00:15:31,040
According to the map's indication,
the Green Lotus Earth Core Flame should be here.

152
00:15:31,040 --> 00:15:33,270
But why can't I find the entrance yet?

153
00:15:33,270 --> 00:15:35,840
We've circled four times already.

154
00:15:35,840 --> 00:15:37,940
Do you have a poor sense of direction?

155
00:15:37,940 --> 00:15:39,860
Husband, don't get anxious.

156
00:15:39,860 --> 00:15:42,850
The more you rush me,
the more I'll be unable to find it.

157
00:15:42,850 --> 00:15:46,120
If we still don't hurry,
Nalan Jie will die from the poison.

158
00:15:51,720 --> 00:15:56,800
Actually, I just want to have more time alone
for just the two of us.

159
00:15:56,800 --> 00:15:58,470
Then...

160
00:15:58,470 --> 00:16:00,950
Th-Then we should still wait
till our official matters are done, right?

161
00:16:00,950 --> 00:16:03,740
W-Why must it be now?

162
00:16:05,330 --> 00:16:08,220
A body distressed with poison within
can only live until thirty years old.

163
00:16:08,220 --> 00:16:10,640
To people like you, perhaps that time
may seem to be very long.

164
00:16:10,640 --> 00:16:15,080
But to me, it is only as long as
a flower blooming just for a Spring

165
00:16:15,080 --> 00:16:17,880
or a little worm living for a Summer.

166
00:16:17,880 --> 00:16:19,620
That won't happen.

167
00:16:19,620 --> 00:16:22,980
I surely will cure your body of the poison within.

168
00:16:24,310 --> 00:16:26,550
I will definitely make you live beyond thirty years old.

169
00:16:28,490 --> 00:16:31,370
Take your time looking for it.
Let's not be anxious.

170
00:16:33,930 --> 00:16:36,100
Husband, you're the best!

171
00:16:37,440 --> 00:16:41,300
I... I... Right now, I feel we...

172
00:16:41,300 --> 00:16:42,890
should...

173
00:16:42,890 --> 00:16:46,740
should head west on that fork in the path
we just passed by.

174
00:16:46,740 --> 00:16:47,830
What? Is that so?

175
00:16:47,830 --> 00:16:49,970
But why do I feel that

176
00:16:49,970 --> 00:16:52,190
we should head north?

177
00:16:52,190 --> 00:16:55,800
It's just my opinion.

178
00:16:56,700 --> 00:16:58,800
Fine, I'll listen to my husband.

179
00:16:58,800 --> 00:17:00,280
Let's go.

180
00:17:01,780 --> 00:17:03,300
Let's go.

181
00:17:19,420 --> 00:17:21,240
- I've found–
- Shhh!

182
00:17:34,829 --> 00:17:36,779
Wait for me out here.

183
00:18:11,000 --> 00:18:12,960
The Queen Medusa...

184
00:18:46,860 --> 00:18:52,400
To Heaven God and Mother Snake in heaven,
I earnestly pray

185
00:18:52,400 --> 00:18:55,590
that you will bless the Snake People Empire
in getting past this calamity.

186
00:18:55,590 --> 00:18:57,680
Even if I die and my body is decimated,

187
00:18:57,680 --> 00:19:01,740
I will protect my homeland and my citizens.

188
00:19:28,330 --> 00:19:31,820
Your Majesty, General Mo Basi asks for an audience!

189
00:19:33,080 --> 00:19:34,710
Come in.

190
00:19:38,240 --> 00:19:41,060
My Queen, I'm incompetent.

191
00:19:41,060 --> 00:19:44,650
General Mo Basi, how's the war situation?

192
00:19:45,600 --> 00:19:49,940
That Mo Clan is really too evil.
They've killed half of the soldiers from our tribe.

193
00:19:49,940 --> 00:19:53,070
I don't know where they've found those
black robed men to assist them.

194
00:19:53,070 --> 00:19:56,950
Right now, they are slowly getting nearer to the palace.

195
00:19:58,480 --> 00:20:01,030
The Mo Clan has been battling us for hundreds of years.

196
00:20:01,030 --> 00:20:03,500
How did they become so strong this time?

197
00:20:03,500 --> 00:20:05,630
Who is helping them?

198
00:20:06,410 --> 00:20:10,000
Looks like... they're from the Blood Sect.

199
00:20:16,310 --> 00:20:21,840
The Mo Clan allied with Soul Hall? So shameless.

200
00:20:24,710 --> 00:20:27,260
I have been in the Fight Emperor Rank for hundreds of years.

201
00:20:27,260 --> 00:20:29,230
Not improving at all.

202
00:20:29,230 --> 00:20:31,910
Only by taking in the Green Lotus Earth Core Flame

203
00:20:31,910 --> 00:20:36,780
will I have the hope of breaking through
to the Fight Ancestor Rank and force the Mo Clan to retreat.

204
00:20:39,720 --> 00:20:41,830
By all means, you can't.

205
00:20:41,830 --> 00:20:45,750
My Queen, the entire Snake People Tribe
is willing to die for you.

206
00:20:45,750 --> 00:20:48,470
You mustn't put yourself in danger.

207
00:20:50,060 --> 00:20:52,600
I've already gathered the most elite troop.

208
00:20:52,600 --> 00:20:55,200
They'll escort you out now.

209
00:20:56,310 --> 00:21:00,330
I was born here. Raised here.

210
00:21:00,330 --> 00:21:04,020
Other than the Snake People Empire,
where else can I go?

211
00:21:04,610 --> 00:21:09,130
My Queen, when the Mo Clan attacks,
they won't leave anyone alive.

212
00:21:09,130 --> 00:21:12,180
They want to totally annihilate our tribe.

213
00:21:13,790 --> 00:21:18,940
I ask you to take care of your precious body.
Leave first and avoid disaster.

214
00:21:18,940 --> 00:21:22,270
Only then can there be a hope of revival for our empire.

215
00:21:23,020 --> 00:21:24,430
No.

216
00:21:25,680 --> 00:21:30,660
I would rather die fighting than surrender like a scoundrel.

217
00:21:32,400 --> 00:21:33,950
Leave now.

218
00:21:34,560 --> 00:21:36,290
My Queen.

219
00:21:42,370 --> 00:21:43,900
Yes.

220
00:22:28,030 --> 00:22:29,890
Who's there?

221
00:22:38,680 --> 00:22:40,180
Who are you?

222
00:22:43,310 --> 00:22:44,900
I'm Xiao Yan.

223
00:22:45,610 --> 00:22:48,310
I'm here to get the Green Lotus Earth Core Flame.

224
00:22:48,310 --> 00:22:50,260
I don't have any other evil intentions.

225
00:22:59,060 --> 00:23:00,930
The Mo Clan has attacked all the way here.

226
00:23:20,610 --> 00:23:22,810
Multicolored Ingesting Heavenly Python?

227
00:23:52,380 --> 00:23:56,040
Queen, I'm taking the Green Lotus Earth Core Flame away.

228
00:24:01,050 --> 00:24:05,310
The Mo Clan will be charging in here soon.
If you continue to stay here,

229
00:24:05,310 --> 00:24:07,330
you'll surely die.

230
00:24:13,580 --> 00:24:18,860
If you trust me, leave with me.
I will surely not harm you.

231
00:24:22,430 --> 00:24:25,340
Queen, there's no time left.

232
00:24:26,510 --> 00:24:28,000
Queen!

233
00:24:41,100 --> 00:24:45,230
Medicine Elder! Medicine Elder!
I have the Green Lotus Earth Core Flame!

234
00:24:45,230 --> 00:24:47,960
So reckless.
You're casually absorbing Essence Flames left and right.

235
00:24:47,960 --> 00:24:51,080
Go out first. I'll help keep it for you first.
Refine it later.

236
00:24:51,080 --> 00:24:52,440
Okay.

237
00:25:09,280 --> 00:25:12,980
Not this way. Let's go...!
Not this way...!

238
00:25:12,980 --> 00:25:16,200
After getting that flame,
you're running quite fast.

239
00:25:19,680 --> 00:25:23,850
Husband, wait up!
Don't you care about me?

240
00:25:24,740 --> 00:25:27,120
Let's go... Hurry.

241
00:25:34,950 --> 00:25:39,300
Husband! Strive a bit harder and we'll be there soon!

242
00:25:44,180 --> 00:25:45,920
Husband!

243
00:26:00,820 --> 00:26:02,640
Husband!

244
00:26:15,160 --> 00:26:18,430
