Quickly dip yourself in that pool.

255
00:27:35,020 --> 00:27:36,550
Calm your emotions!

256
00:27:36,550 --> 00:27:41,380
Your blood, flesh, bone, and internal organs
will be burned to ashes.

257
00:27:41,380 --> 00:27:44,160
Then, reconstruct them while in the fire.

258
00:27:51,110 --> 00:27:54,010
If you can't take it, spit out the fire.

259
00:28:11,260 --> 00:28:15,220
You just want to torment yourself, is that it?
Fine, let me tell you.

260
00:28:15,220 --> 00:28:17,520
Don't counter the direction of the Essence Flame.

261
00:28:17,520 --> 00:28:22,030
If the Essence Flame counterattacks,
you will never get out of this Spatial Ring.

262
00:28:23,990 --> 00:28:29,480
Now, I'm going to defend your heart and vital channels.
Focus and observe.

263
00:28:49,010 --> 00:28:50,790
Hey!

264
00:28:54,560 --> 00:28:57,460
Husband! Husband!

265
00:28:59,780 --> 00:29:01,700
Husband!

266
00:29:02,690 --> 00:29:04,330
Husband!

267
00:29:06,500 --> 00:29:08,560
Husband, are you all right?

268
00:29:09,670 --> 00:29:13,150
