272
00:30:38,960 --> 00:30:42,140
Medicine Elder, you've worked hard.

273
00:30:43,610 --> 00:30:46,340
An extraordinary person will achieve the extraordinary feat.

274
00:30:46,340 --> 00:30:49,110
