296
00:32:55,270 --> 00:32:57,300
We'll do another treatment tomorrow

297
00:32:57,300 --> 00:33:02,320
and it will be totally cured. It's just that this poison has been
in your body for so long it has entered deep into your organs.

298
00:33:02,320 --> 00:33:06,620
