it might cause great damage to your Fight Qi.

299
00:33:07,320 --> 00:33:10,210
Being able to preserve one's life is already a great fortune.

300
00:33:10,210 --> 00:33:12,450
Don't put too much importance on Fight Qi.

301
00:33:13,810 --> 00:33:19,370
Mister Yan Xiao, I won't express my thanks to you too much.

302
00:33:19,370 --> 00:33:23,950
But I will never forget that you saved me today.

303
00:33:23,950 --> 00:33:28,050
The Nalan Clan will be sure to handsomely reward you.

304
00:33:29,190 --> 00:33:33,430
It's just that there's still one thing I don't understand.
I would like to ask you about it.

305
00:33:34,530 --> 00:33:36,230
Please speak.

306
00:33:41,620 --> 00:33:46,460
Mister Yan Xiao, you're still very young, yet you already
have two different Essence Flames in your body.

307
00:33:46,460 --> 00:33:49,860
One kind is a Beast Flame.
Forgive me for being ignorant.

308
00:33:49,860 --> 00:33:53,060
May I ask who your master is?

309
00:33:59,160 --> 00:34:03,930
Forgive me for being rudely frank.
You seem to be meddling too much.

310
00:34:07,240 --> 00:34:12,490
My whole life, I made it my utmost duty
to unite the clans of the nation

311
00:34:12,490 --> 00:34:15,230
to fight against Soul Hall.

312
00:34:15,230 --> 00:34:18,810
Today, I was careless to have fallen
for a measly poisoning trick.

313
00:34:18,810 --> 00:34:23,510
If I were to die in their hands today,
it would be due to my destiny.

314
00:34:23,510 --> 00:34:28,050
But I have never owed anyone any favor.

315
00:34:28,600 --> 00:34:32,570
If Mister Yan Xiao has connections with Soul Hall,

316
00:34:32,570 --> 00:34:35,420
or if it was Soul Hall that sent you here,

317
00:34:35,420 --> 00:34:40,840
I'd rather die in your hands
than accept any further treatment.

318
00:34:51,659 --> 00:34:54,179
For Elder Nalan to voice such intentions,

319
00:34:54,179 --> 00:34:57,349
my efforts were not in vain.

320
00:34:57,350 --> 00:35:00,159
You don't have to worry about my identity.

321
00:35:00,159 --> 00:35:04,919
Just like you, I have a bloody grudge against Soul Hall also.

322
00:35:10,340 --> 00:35:13,080
Mister Yan Xiao, you have worked hard.
Please go to the front hall to have some tea.

323
00:35:13,080 --> 00:35:14,640
