324
00:35:15,840 --> 00:35:21,550
Can I ask Mister Yan Xiao to remove your mask
and let me see your face?

325
00:35:25,100 --> 00:35:29,430
Grandfather, you've just recovered.
It's better that you rest first.

326
00:35:29,430 --> 00:35:33,290
Take good care of Elder Nalan. I'll return tomorrow.

327
00:36:17,860 --> 00:36:21,490
Lad, we meet again.

328
00:36:21,490 --> 00:36:23,290
Fan Lao?

329
00:36:24,250 --> 00:36:26,670
You finally appeared.

330
00:36:26,670 --> 00:36:29,270
I urge you to stop being meddlesome.

331
00:36:29,270 --> 00:36:33,370
It's very easy for me to kill you.

332
00:36:34,480 --> 00:36:35,860
You can try.

333
00:36:35,860 --> 00:36:38,010
