334
00:36:38,010 --> 00:36:39,590
Xiao Yan!

335
00:36:48,920 --> 00:36:50,450
Xiao Yan.

336
00:36:55,260 --> 00:36:57,200
Elder Tengshan.

337
00:36:57,200 --> 00:37:02,250
Earlier, Nalan Jie's illness suddenly relapsed
and it almost harmed his heart.

338
00:37:02,250 --> 00:37:05,540
What? How?

339
00:37:05,540 --> 00:37:09,190
When you were treating him,
did you notice anything strange?

340
00:37:11,230 --> 00:37:15,490
The poison in his body has worsened compared to the time
before I went to Snake People Empire.

341
00:37:15,490 --> 00:37:18,210
It shows that in these past few days,

342
00:37:18,210 --> 00:37:21,890
